      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines the format of a new Resource Record (RR) for the Domain Naming System (DNS), and reserves a corresponding DNS type mnemonic and numerical code.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.  This memo does not specify an Internet standard of any kind.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
